Title: First Massive State of the Superstring in Superspace
Authors: N. Berkovits and M.M. Leite (IFT/UNESP, Sao Paulo)
Comments: 7 pages latex
Report-no: IFT-P.057/97
Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B415 (1997) 144-148
\\
  Using the manifestly spacetime supersymmetric description of the
four-dimensional open superstring, we construct the vertex operator in
superspace for the first massive state. This construction provides an N=1 D=4
superspace representation of the massive spin-2 multiplet.
